statements: SELECT id, account_holder_name, retirement_account_type, age, distribution_amount FROM required_minimum_distributions;
SELECT account_holder_name, age, distribution_amount, retirement_account_type, id FROM required_minimum_distributions;
SELECT retirement_account_type, distribution_amount, age, account_holder_name, id FROM required_minimum_distributions;
SELECT account_holder_name, distribution_amount, id, retirement_account_type, age FROM required_minimum_distributions;
SELECT id, retirement_account_type, distribution_amount, account_holder_name, age FROM required_minimum_distributions;
SELECT * FROM required_minimum_distributions WHERE age > 65 ORDER BY retirement_account_type DESC, distribution_amount ASC LIMIT 10
SELECT account_holder_name, SUM(distribution_amount) AS total_distributions FROM required_minimum_distributions GROUP BY account_holder_name HAVING SUM(distribution_amount) > 10000
SELECT id, account_holder_name, distribution_amount FROM required_minimum_distributions WHERE retirement_account_type = '401(k)' AND age > 70 ORDER BY distribution_amount DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT AVG(distribution_amount) AS average_distribution, retirement_account_type FROM required_minimum_distributions GROUP BY retirement_account_type HAVING AVG(distribution_amount) > 5000
SELECT account_holder_name, MAX(age) AS max_age, MIN(age) AS min_age FROM required_minimum_distributions GROUP BY account_holder_name ORDER BY max_age DESC
SELECT * FROM retirement_accounts;
SELECT ra_id, account_holder_name, account_balance FROM retirement_accounts;
SELECT account_holder_name, age FROM retirement_accounts ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT ra_id, required_min_distribution FROM distribution_calculations WHERE calculation_date = '2022-12-31';
SELECT ra_id, account_balance, age FROM retirement_accounts WHERE account_balance > 10000 ORDER BY account_balance DESC;
SELECT * FROM retirement_accounts WHERE age > 50 ORDER BY account_balance DESC;
SELECT ra.account_holder_name, dc.required_min_distribution FROM retirement_accounts ra JOIN distribution_calculations dc ON ra.ra_id = dc.ra_id;
SELECT account_holder_name, age FROM retirement_accounts WHERE account_balance > 100000 ORDER BY age;
SELECT * FROM distribution_calculations WHERE calculation_date = '2022-08-15';
SELECT ra.account_holder_name, dc.required_min_distribution, ra.age FROM retirement_accounts ra JOIN distribution_calculations dc ON ra.ra_id = dc.ra_id WHERE dc.required_min_distribution > 5000;
SELECT * FROM retirement_account;
SELECT account_owner, account_balance FROM retirement_account ORDER BY account_balance DESC;
SELECT account_owner, account_balance FROM retirement_account WHERE account_balance > 5000;
SELECT account_owner, account_age FROM retirement_account WHERE account_age BETWEEN 50 AND 60;
SELECT account_owner, SUM(distribution_amount) AS total_distribution FROM distribution_events GROUP BY account_id;
SELECT * FROM retirement_account ORDER BY account_balance DESC, account_owner
SELECT account_owner, account_age, account_balance FROM retirement_account WHERE account_age > 50 ORDER BY account_age

SELECT account_owner, SUM(distribution_amount) AS total_distribution FROM retirement_account JOIN distribution_events ON retirement_account.account_id = distribution_events.account_id GROUP BY account_owner
SELECT * FROM distribution_events WHERE event_date >= '2022-01-01' AND distribution_amount > 1000 ORDER BY event_date DESC

SELECT account_owner, distribution_percentage FROM retirement_account JOIN distribution_rules ON retirement_account.account_age >= distribution_rules.age_threshold ORDER BY distribution_percentage DESC
SELECT * FROM account_holders
SELECT name, birthdate FROM account_holders WHERE account_holder_id = 1
SELECT account_balance, open_date FROM retirement_accounts ORDER BY account_balance DESC
SELECT * FROM distribution_rules WHERE age_requirement > 65
SELECT account_id, distribution_amount FROM distributions WHERE distribution_date = '2022-01-15'
SELECT * FROM account_holders WHERE name = 'John Doe';
SELECT account_holder_id, name FROM account_holders WHERE birthdate BETWEEN '1980-01-01' AND '1990-12-31';
SELECT account_holder_id, account_balance FROM retirement_accounts WHERE account_balance > 10000;
SELECT * FROM distribution_rules WHERE age_requirement >= 65 ORDER BY distribution_percentage DESC;
SELECT account_id, distribution_amount, distribution_date FROM distributions WHERE distribution_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY distribution_amount DESC;
SELECT * FROM required_min_distributions;
SELECT account_id, age FROM required_min_distributions;
SELECT * FROM account_owners WHERE owner_id = 1;
SELECT owner_name, account_id FROM account_owners WHERE owner_id = 2;
SELECT beneficiary_name, account_id FROM beneficiaries WHERE beneficiary_id = 3;
SELECT * FROM required_min_distributions ORDER BY age DESC, distribution_amount ASC;
SELECT beneficiary_name, amount_distributed FROM beneficiaries JOIN distribution_history ON beneficiaries.account_id = distribution_history.account_id WHERE amount_distributed > 500;
SELECT owner_name, balance FROM account_owners JOIN account_balances ON account_owners.account_id = account_balances.account_id WHERE owner_name LIKE 'J%';
SELECT AVG(distribution_amount) FROM required_min_distributions;
SELECT account_id, distribution_date FROM distribution_history ORDER BY distribution_date DESC LIMIT 5;
